About This Project

Global warming is a serious issue in our world. In a rapidly changing environment, it is hard to keep track of all of our effects on the world. An example of this is climate change. By viewing the trends in the sea levels, carbon dioxide levels, and temperature levels, we can see how much of an impact climate change has on our world. This project provides a visualization of these levels and allows you to understand the seriousness of the currenet issue.
